| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1557 — Recovery Inhibition (arcusmedia)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 9f1142dc-3d2f-5a68-8ad4-af6939adb9a0"
